      <trans-unit xml:space="preserve" id="4aa4330d4cda2e02" weblate-flags="md-text, safe-html, strict-same">
        <source>Interaction: Chimeras are a lot like wild animals with rabies. They’re confused and violent, and they behave erratically. Savage, ferocious beasts, they hate all other creatures and seize any opportunity to kill.</source>
